## Architecture Overview

```
CropDiagnosisPlatform/
├── agrovisus_simulation_engine/    ← Core engine (COMPLETE)
│   ├── app/
│   │   ├── models/                 ← Crop, Soil, Nutrient, Disease models
│   │   ├── services/               ← Simulation, Weather, ET0, Reports
│   │   ├── env/                    ← RL Gymnasium environment
│   │   ├── utils/                  ← Validators, exceptions, calculations
│   │   └── templates/              ← Jinja2 HTML report templates
│   ├── tests/                      ← 8 test files, 60+ tests
│   ├── outputs/                    ← Simulation CSV + HTML reports
│   ├── dashboard.py                ← Streamlit dashboard
│   ├── run.py                      ← CLI simulation runner
│   └── scenario_runner.py          ← Batch crop comparison
│
├── backend/                        ← FastAPI API (SCAFFOLDED)
│   ├── main.py                     ← App entry point
│   └── routers/                    ← simulation, disease, crops
│
├── frontend/                       ← Vite + React (SCAFFOLDED)
│   └── src/pages/                  ← Landing, Simulate, Disease, Reports
│
├── models/                         ← Trained AI models
│   ├── best_model.pth              ← CNN (~67MB)
│   └── ppo/                        ← PPO RL agent
│
├── MVP_PLAN.md                     ← 4-week sprint plan
└── FUTURE_ARCHITECTURE_REDESIGN.md ← Post-funding architecture
```

